        }

        --- Signature: function InvalidByteError(value : String) : String
        --- Returns: String.
        --- Summary: Provides the stdlib invalid byte error operation using current Klang data types and runtime helpers.
        --- Contract: Preserve this typed interface when upgrading to a runtime-backed implementation.
